Lucian Name Meaning in English

What does the name Lucian mean? What is the meaning of the name Lucian, lucky number, lucky stone, origin and religion.

Lucien is a male given name of French origin, meaning light. It is the French form of Luciano or Latin Lucianus, patronymic of Lucius.
